00057 void initialize(MSData& msd)
00058 {
00059     SpectrumListSimplePtr sl(new SpectrumListSimple);
00060     msd.run.spectrumListPtr = sl;
00061 
00062     for (size_t i=0; i<5; i++)
00063     {
00064         SpectrumPtr spectrum(new Spectrum);
00065         sl->spectra.push_back(spectrum);
00066         spectrum->index = i;
00067         spectrum->nativeID = lexical_cast<string>(18+(int)i);
00068         spectrum->spectrumDescription.scan.cvParams.push_back(CVParam(MS_scan_time, 420+i, MS_second));
00069         spectrum->setMZIntensityPairs((MZIntensityPair*)data_[i], 7);
00070     }
00071 }

00099 void testConfig(const RegionAnalyzer::Config& config)
00100 {
00101     MSData msd;
00102     initialize(msd);
00103 
00104     shared_ptr<MSDataCache> cache(new MSDataCache);
00105     shared_ptr<RegionAnalyzer> regionAnalyzer(new RegionAnalyzer(config, *cache));
00106 
00107     MSDataAnalyzerContainer analyzers;
00108     analyzers.push_back(cache);
00109     analyzers.push_back(regionAnalyzer);
00110 
00111     MSDataAnalyzerDriver driver(analyzers);
00112     driver.analyze(msd);
00113 
00114     unit_assert(regionAnalyzer->spectrumStats().size() == 5);
00115 
00116     if (os_) *os_ << "sumIntensity (max) (peak):\n";
00117 
00118     vector<RegionAnalyzer::SpectrumStats>::const_iterator it = 
00119         regionAnalyzer->spectrumStats().begin();
00120     if (os_) *os_ << *it << endl;
00121     unit_assert(it->sumIntensity == 0);
00122     unit_assert_equal(it->max.mz, 0, epsilon_);
00123     unit_assert_equal(it->max.intensity, 0, epsilon_);
00124     unit_assert_equal(it->peak.mz, 0, epsilon_);
00125     unit_assert_equal(it->peak.intensity, 0, epsilon_);
00126 
00127     ++it;
00128     if (os_) *os_ << *it << endl;
00129     unit_assert(it->sumIntensity == 5);
00130     unit_assert_equal(it->max.mz, 3.1, epsilon_);
00131     unit_assert_equal(it->max.intensity, 2, epsilon_);
00132     unit_assert_equal(it->peak.mz, 3.1, epsilon_);
00133     unit_assert_equal(it->peak.intensity, 2, epsilon_);
00134 
00135     ++it;
00136     if (os_) *os_ << *it << endl;
00137     unit_assert(it->sumIntensity == 6); // with omitted sample intensity 4
00138     unit_assert_equal(it->max.mz, 1.9, epsilon_);
00139     unit_assert_equal(it->max.intensity, 3, epsilon_);
00140     unit_assert_equal(it->peak.mz, 2.9, epsilon_); // found the peak by interpolation
00141     unit_assert_equal(it->peak.intensity, 4, epsilon_);
00142 
00143     ++it;
00144     if (os_) *os_ << *it << endl;
00145     unit_assert(it->sumIntensity == 5);
00146     unit_assert_equal(it->max.mz, 3.1, epsilon_);
00147     unit_assert_equal(it->max.intensity, 2, epsilon_);
00148     unit_assert_equal(it->peak.mz, 3.1, epsilon_);
00149     unit_assert_equal(it->peak.intensity, 2, epsilon_);
00150 
00151     ++it;
00152     if (os_) *os_ << *it << endl;
00153     unit_assert(it->sumIntensity == 0);
00154     unit_assert_equal(it->max.mz, 0, epsilon_);
00155     unit_assert_equal(it->max.intensity, 0, epsilon_);
00156     unit_assert_equal(it->peak.mz, 0, epsilon_);
00157     unit_assert_equal(it->peak.intensity, 0, epsilon_);
00158 
00159     // Stats
00160 
00161     const RegionAnalyzer::Stats& stats = regionAnalyzer->stats();
00162     if (os_) *os_ << stats << endl; 
00163     unit_assert(stats.nonzeroCount == 3);
00164     unit_assert_equal(stats.sum_sumIntensity, 16, epsilon_);
00165     unit_assert_equal(stats.sum_peak_intensity, 8, epsilon_);
00166     unit_assert_equal(stats.mean_peak_mz, 3, epsilon_);
00167     unit_assert_equal(stats.variance_peak_mz, .01, epsilon_);
00168     unit_assert_equal(stats.sd_peak_mz, .1, epsilon_);
00169     unit_assert(stats.indexApex == 2);
